of the Hellenic Coast Guard for 17 years. For the last 5 years I am working as a skipper, mostly with sailing boats. I am Greek, Non Smoker, I love cooking, exploring and learning about new countries and cultures I have got Offshore sailing diploma, Motor boat diploma up to 100kor, Cosmos Nautical Academy courses for firefighting-survival first aid and crisis management."},{"name":"Victoria Makovska","avatar":"/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca488-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::abbb2b70-acf5-11ef-b776-07205becc711/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Victoria was born in Ukraine and raised between Ukraine Germany and Russia. She has been living in Greece for the past 23 years. She has 20 years of working experience in customer service making sure everybody meets their requests. Always smiling, filling up the place with her positive energy and calmness."},{"name":"Carlos George","avatar":"/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca488-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::c1ddd380-acf5-11ef-aa4e-6124c6446a3d/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Carlos is a highly qualified sailor with great sailing experience in Greek waters. Always calm and confident with the will to help everyone on board to enjoy and be part of the sailing experience.. Always positive and willing to do the best for the crew and the guests. He wants to share with people the joy of the water element. His dream is to visit many places and make friends all around the world."}],"pricing":{"weekPricingFrom":{"currency":"EUR","price":2200000,"displayCurrency":"EUR","displayPrice":2200000,"unit":"WEEK"},"weekPricingTo":{"currency":"EUR","price":3000000,"displayCurrency":"EUR","displayPrice":3000000,"unit":"WEEK"},"pricingInfo":[{"name":"Low Season","effectiveDates":[],"pricing":{"currency":"EUR","charterFee":2200000,"inputAmountTaxed":"EXCLUSIVE","note":"","unit":"WEEK","lineItems":[{"item":"Charter Fee","quantity":1,"unitPrice":2200000,"amount":2200000,"conditions":"Weekly","taxRate":{"label":"VA